:::tacticExample
{goal show:=false}`∀ (i j k : Nat), i < j → j < k → i < k`
```setup
intro i j k h1 h2
```
In this proof state:
```pre
i j k : Nat
h1 : i < j
h2 : j < k
⊢ i < k
```

invoking {tacticStep}`apply?` suggests:

```tacticOutput
Try this: exact Nat.lt_trans h1 h2
```

